                <div class="about-description">
                    <p>Hi, I'm Izhan, a 12th-grade student and full-stack developer from Kashmir. I created Mindfullness with the vision of making mental health support accessible to everyone through innovative technology.</p>
                    <br>
                    <p>As a young developer, I believe in the power of technology to create positive change. Mindfullness represents my commitment to combining cutting-edge AI with compassionate mental health support.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="skills-section">
                    <h3>Technical Skills</h3>
                    <div class="skills-grid">
                        <div class="skill-item" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">
                            <i class="fab fa-node-js skill-icon"></i>
                            <p>Node.js</p>
